    <a href="/case-studies/07-axs-ai-architecture">three-layer AI
    architecture</a>, the metadata an MCP server can serve, an IDE
    can autocomplete, and an agent can reason over. The other two layers
    (the MCP server itself, and Claude Code skills) sit on top of this.
  </p>

  <hr class="jm-rule" />

  <h2 class="section-title">component scaffolder (axs-automation:create-component)</h2>
